    <note>Guo(1) Zhizhong [19471] Yuanfu coalition. CBD has Huating, rather than Huayang, resident. He was purged and lived in Chengzhou, Tonggu (modern Chengxian) county during his 12 year exile -- which also makes the Sichuan address more likely than Huating (modern Songjiang). He raised a militia to defend Chengzhou against the Jin attack in ca. 1131. Sichuan TZ, 122.34b. Kinship based on address, generational name and chronological logic. CBD, 3, 2146.</note>
